de.dosmike.sponge.megamenus.api.state

Class StateObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.dosmike.sponge.megamenus.api.state.StateObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class StateObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This is a generic state that can be attached to a menu. It is meant to store smaller data. Generally these states do not persis, but you can get and set them to menus at any time.
